description.jei_compat.invisibility_shie: This peculiar shield can help you a lot in fights against your enemies, in fact you can easily hold right-click to block damage and to become invisible, from that moment on as long as you hold right click mobs won't notice you. When you release right-click the lemurite shield will be on a cooldown for a period of time depending on the time you used the shield. There's a shield use limit of 30 seconds after which the shield is automatically put on cooldown.
description.jei_compat.tar_processing: Tar is generated in the world in a liquid form (Liquid Tar), however if it's kept away from the other tar fluid blocks it cools down becoming Tar Ore, that you can mine to get both the item form of Tar and occasionally Bitumen
description.jei_compat.thermite: Thermite dust can be melted in Tinkers' Construct's smeltery and then used in the smeltery tank to fuel it, this enhanced fuel allows you to melt ores you couldn't smelt before and to smelt usual ores way faster than when you use lava.
effect.metallurgy.punch_effect_tired: ยง4You are too tired! Eat something first!
